{"title": "Rainfall", "html": "<section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container has_text_color\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner us_custom_6df4bc3a \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h4><strong>Rainfall Monitoring Stations and Records</strong></h4>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_color\" data-bg-override=\"0\" data-bg-color=\"#506677\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-vc-row=\"\"  data-vc=\"6.1\"  data-is_old_vc=\"\"  data-theme-support=\"\"   data-overlay=\"false\" data-overlay-color=\"\" data-overlay-pattern=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-opacity=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-size=\"\"    ></div><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>This page contains links to historic and current rainfall data. Some records extend back to 1921. Most data collection ceased during the war but some has recommenced as a result of commercial developments and publically funded projects including the Water Security Project. As more rainfall data comes to light it will be posted on this page.</h5>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small with_line width_default thick_2 style_dashed color_primary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_auto\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h3>Key</h3>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Site Reference Numbers</h5>\n<p>Site reference number prefixes that are used link back to the maps generated in the 2015 Water Security Report:</p>\n<p><strong>Riv</strong><br />\nMap 2, Proposed River Monitoring Network<br />\n<strong>Met</strong><br />\nMap 3, Proposed Meteorological Monitoring Network<br />\n<strong>SN, AD, MD, BD, Teko</strong><br />\nMap 10, Rokel-Seli River Basin Water Security Project</p>\n<p><em>* Those not prefixed are not shown on report maps. See Lists and Maps in </em><a href=\"https://fb615793-e8b4-4c13-9093-8c3cb093f037.filesusr.com/ugd/bf9204_ede82d8d30354dbab0041188775368fc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Volume 1 Appendices.</em></a></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Included Data</h5>\n<p>The types of data that are included in the downloads are indicated in the charts below as follows:</p>\n<p><strong>R</strong> Rainfall<br />\n<strong>G</strong> Groundwater Level<br />\n<strong>F</strong> Stream or River Flow<br />\n<strong>B</strong> Barometric Pressure<br />\n<strong>Tw</strong> Water Temperature<br />\n<strong>Ta</strong> Air Temperature</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Data Owner, Collector or Origin</h5>\n<p>The data is made available from different sources which is listed in the charts below:</p>\n<p><strong>ADDAX</strong> Addax Biosciences<br />\n<strong>BWMA</strong> Bumbuna Watershed Management Authority<br />\n<strong>Met Dept</strong> Meteorological Department<br />\n<strong>MOE</strong> Ministry of Energy<br />\n<strong>MWR</strong> Ministry of Water Resources</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div id=\"i7xj42ea\" class=\"txtNew\" data-packed=\"true\">\n<h5 class=\"font_2\">Consolidated Rainfall Records (1941 to 1960 and 2012 onwards)</h5>\n</div>\n</div></div><div  class=\"vc_wp_text wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"widget widget_text\">\t\t\t<div class=\"textwidget\"><table id=\"tablepress-5\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-5 tablepress-responsive\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n<th class=\"column-1\">Monitoring Site Location or Name</th>\n<th class=\"column-2\">Included Data</th>\n<th class=\"column-3\">Data Owner</th>\n<th class=\"column-4\">Data Collection or Origin</th>\n<th class=\"column-5\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">Rainfall Statistics 38 Stations 1941-1960 (Gregory 1965)</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">R</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">Author</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">Various</td>\n<td class=\"column-5\"><a href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/Rainfall-Statistics-38-Stations-1941-1960-Gregory-1965.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"document\" id=\"i84gx17olink\" class=\"g-transparent-a b2link\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span id=\"i84gx17ola